.board-contents-float(ng-show='!player.ready')
  button(ng-click='ready()', class='btn btn-success') Ready
.board-contents(ng-show='player.ready && !game') Waiting for other players...
  button(ng-click='startNow()', class='btn btn-success', ng-show='player.master')
.board-contents(ng-show='game && !letters') The game will start in:
  h3 {{preStartTimeLeft}}
.board-contents(ng-show='letters')
  table
    tr(ng-repeat='lettersRow in letters')
      td(ng-repeat='letter in lettersRow track by $index') {{letter}}